_time_low":26.75,"long_business_summary":"Maruti Interior Products Limited manufactures, sells, and exports modular kitchen storage systems under the Everyday Kitchen and Spitze brands. The company's products include vertical storage, corner storage, drawer pull-outs, inserts, slim tandem drawers, wardrobe accessories, slides and hinges, wardrobe long handles, wooden handles, cabinet profile handle, gola profiles, roller shutters, cabinet lift up, legs, and food waste bins and disposer. It provides customized wire racks, oven wire grills, custom wire-formed products and components, laser cutting components, etc. The company was formerly known as Ravi Bearings Private Limited and changed its name to Maruti Interior Products Limited in May 2000. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Rajkot, India."}}